    /* v6.3 polish — enforce ≥ 44×44 tap target on every hero__link.
       The audit flagged "Resume ↓", "Selected work", "Methodology (G1–G31)"
       at 88×33 / 109×24 / 181×24 px. Vertical padding of 0.5rem on
       each side lifts the click rect to ≥ 44 px tall without shifting
       the visible baseline (text-underline-offset keeps the underline
       in place). */
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    min-height: 44px;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    transition:
      color var(--transition),
